WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:16.762 --> 00:00:18.194
I'm happy,
extremely happy,

00:00:18.448 --> 00:00:20.609
this is a huge team
with a huge infrastructure,

00:00:20.959 --> 00:00:22.776
which has great athletes...

00:00:22.777 --> 00:00:23.886
and a good project.

00:00:24.071 --> 00:00:25.760
I hope I manage
to be happy here as well,

00:00:25.761 --> 00:00:27.939
I'll do my best to honor this jersey,

00:00:28.351 --> 00:00:29.375
and, consequently,

00:00:29.376 --> 00:00:31.265
play well and win trophies.

00:00:31.376 --> 00:00:34.188
Some of my friends
used to talk about the club,

00:00:34.189 --> 00:00:37.378
athletes that used to play here
and some that still play,

00:00:37.566 --> 00:00:38.948
saying that the club
has a great infrastructure,

00:00:38.949 --> 00:00:41.468
I took a look around and the club
has everything we need,

00:00:42.008 --> 00:00:44.485
and that will help us
to do our best.

00:00:44.486 --> 00:00:48.337
It's always important to have
some references about the club,

00:00:48.338 --> 00:00:52.020
about the employees,
the Board of Directors,

00:00:52.479 --> 00:00:54.482
Victor Ferraz even called me,

00:00:54.483 --> 00:00:58.033
he said I could come because this is
a huge team with a huge infrastructure,

00:00:58.084 --> 00:00:59.723
that I'd like it very much,

00:01:00.271 --> 00:01:02.785
that all the players
would welcome me,

00:01:02.786 --> 00:01:03.618
and that's what I did,

00:01:04.297 --> 00:01:06.311
now I'm here
and I hope to be very happy.

00:01:21.747 --> 00:01:23.914
It's a good squad,
the team's base was preserved,

00:01:23.915 --> 00:01:27.045
the players that come from
the Youth Academy are very qualified,

00:01:27.046 --> 00:01:28.956
there are also experienced
and extremely qualified players,

00:01:28.957 --> 00:01:30.801
as well as an experienced
Coaching Staff,

00:01:31.362 --> 00:01:34.970
the Board of Directors is working
to honor the club,

00:01:34.971 --> 00:01:37.343
doing everything they can.

00:01:37.870 --> 00:01:39.775
I hope that,
as we get to know each other,

00:01:40.041 --> 00:01:43.787
and with all these great players
that are coming,

00:01:43.788 --> 00:01:45.257
we manage to dispute titles,

00:01:45.713 --> 00:01:48.336
it couldn't be any different,

00:01:48.337 --> 00:01:50.404
everyone has to keep
the same goal in mind,

00:01:50.405 --> 00:01:52.051
which is to achieve victories
and win titles.

00:01:52.277 --> 00:01:54.943
It's a pleasure to come
to a huge team such as Santos FC,

00:01:55.107 --> 00:01:56.536
with wonderful fans,

00:01:57.061 --> 00:01:59.296
I hope I manage to do my best...

00:01:59.297 --> 00:02:01.290
so that I can be
applauded by our fans,

00:02:01.291 --> 00:02:03.933
and, together, we are going
to do great things for Santos FC.

